<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .case-details {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Helpdesk Support</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Helpdesk Team,</p>
       </br>
      <p>We wanted to inform you that a new Urgent-priority case has been created in Salesforce. The details of the case are as follows:</p>
      <div class="case-details">
        <p><strong>Case Number:</strong> <a href="{!Case.Link}"> {!Case.CaseNumber}</a></p>
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {!Case.Subject}</p>
        <p><strong>Priority:</strong> {!Case.Priority}</p>
        <p><strong>Requestor Name:</strong> {!Case.Case_Requestor__c}</p>
      </div>
      <p>This case requires immediate attention. Please review the case and take the necessary actions to provide a timely resolution.</p>
</br>
      <p>Best Regards,</p>
      <p>Helpdesk Support Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>